SPECIFIC FRICTION POINTS & FIXES
FRICTION #1: No Pricing Discovery Path
Current State: Hours of operation and facility info visible; pricing nowhere
Impact: Cold leads must call or visit to quote value
Fix:

Embed live pricing widget on homepage
"Current Rates" pinned header link
Price sparklines on material cards (30-day trends)


FRICTION #2: Compliance Documentation Feels Like Barrier
Current State: "Restricted Materials" page is a wall of legal text (538.26 Florida Statute)
Impact: Overwhelms residential suppliers; looks corporate/unwelcoming
Fix:

Break into visual sections: "Don't Bring These" with icons
Create a simple checklist: â˜ Copper radiators â˜ Electrical wire âœ… OK
Highlight "Anything marked with government logo = NO" with example photos
Add FAQ: "Will you reject my load? (Usually not; here's why...)"


FRICTION #3: No Mobile Optimization Signals
Current State: Horizontal nav, tightly spaced elements
Impact: Mobile users likely bounce quickly
Fix:

Hamburger menu for mobile (obviously)
Larger tap targets (48px minimum)
Simplified mobile hero (text only, not video)
Sticky mobile footer with phone CTA


FRICTION #4: Contact Form Generic
Current State: Standard "First Name | Last Name | Email | Phone | Address | Message"
Impact: No value prop, no reason to believe you'll get response
Fix:
[Contact Form Reimagined]
"Get Your Quote in Under 5 Minutes"

