FRICTION #5: No Trust Signals Above Fold
Current State: Hours, contact info, then straight to hero
Impact: New visitors don't know if this is professional/safe/fair
Fix:

Trust bar (sticky): ISRI Member | BBB Accredited A+ | Licensed & Bonded | Est. 2017
Customer testimonial as sidebar on homepage
Google Review stars (link to reviews)
"We've paid out $X million to suppliers" stat


VISUAL DESIGN RECOMMENDATIONS (Technical Details)
Color System Refinement
Proposed Palette (Maintaining Brand, Increasing Sophistication):

Primary Navy: #0A3161 (current, keep)
Secondary (Accent): Emerald Green #10B981 (sustainability signal, replaces scattered colors)
Tertiary: Warm Bronze #B55D60 (for call-to-action buttons, trust-building)
Neutral Dark: #1F2937 (replaces harsh black for better readability)
Neutral Light: #F8F9FA (off-white for breathing room)

Retire:

Lime green (#CCFF00) â†’ Replace with softer sage or remove entirely
Rainbow swoosh â†’ Keep in logo only; simplify elsewhere

Typography System
Headline Stack:

H1: Inter Bold, 52px, tracking 0.5px (modern, clean)
H2: Inter SemiBold, 36px (remove italics)
H3: Inter Medium, 24px

Body Copy:

System font stack: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif
Base: 16px (accessibility), line-height 1.6 (readability)
Remove italics from form labels; use color/weight instead

Spacing & Grid

8px baseline grid (improves consistency)
Container width: 1200px (balanced for industrial imagery)
Margin/padding scale: 8, 16, 24, 32, 48, 64px


