ACCESSIBILITY IMPROVEMENTS (WCAG 2.1 AA Compliance)

 Increase contrast on black background text (aim for 7:1 minimum)
 Remove or reduce italic usage in headers
 Add visible focus states on all interactive elements
 Form labels: Always visible, not italicized, clear association
 Alt text for all material images (descriptive: "Copper radiator coils, clean condition")
 Video captions (facility tour video)
 Keyboard navigation: Test Tab order on all interactive elements
 Color is never the only indicator (e.g., status badges should use icon + color + text)


